{"tid":1866794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】富士康設口罩生產線 日產200萬隻","createTime":"2020-02-07T01:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T02:11:31.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec67733ba3729736f0b67959c2f43007ff4b26f1","tid":1866794,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:48:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1581038779420&amp;issue=20200207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1581038779420%26issue%3D20200207&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=bd14d6ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1581038779420&amp;issue=20200207</a><br />\n<br />\n日經新聞引述蘋果公司的供應商富士康在微信公眾號發布的文章指，富士康導入口罩生產線生產醫用口罩，並且要求在台灣的員工簽署返回內地同意書，力爭在內地的工廠周一恢復生產。<br />\n<br />\n2月5日在深圳的龍華園區順利實現口罩試產；計劃在月底達到日產200萬隻，目前正在申請產品資格認證。<br />\n<br />\n日經新聞引述消息稱，地方政府還要求富士康保證為員工提供足夠的防護設備和資源，才能獲得恢復生產的許可，即使富士康於2月10日恢復生產，蘋果的iPhone產量仍可能受到人手不足的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我擒日先話最有條件改生產口罩既就係富士康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbdfa91547a512cc3986eb6aab0c2d7a87de7be","tid":1866794,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:50:28.000Z","msg":"賣口罩好賺過iphone"},{"pid":"6ba6c5c71cbe99280cbdc286302057691ba5d647","tid":1866794,"uid":71657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"大陸仲爆緊<br />\n仲係大陸工廠生產係咪好事嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口罩衛生同員工健康點保證？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3b61eaf8216e71c67c199534c6a51f6ba412b6","tid":1866794,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:51:00.000Z","msg":"香港人繼續死排<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2hPSSda.png\" data-thumbnail-src